      <url>/posts/12351/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="python简单的运用"><a href="#python简单的运用" class="headerlink" title="python简单的运用"></a>python简单的运用</h2><h3 id="1-利用math库求圆的周长和面积"><a href="#1-利用math库求圆的周长和面积" class="headerlink" title="1.利用math库求圆的周长和面积"></a>1.利用math库求圆的周长和面积</h3><p>我们需要导入pi（就是派），然后再利用公式进行计算<br>为了更好的学习，我们必须掌握一定的词汇量，所以我们的变量都用英语全称来写<br>越早熟悉越好</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">半径：radius</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">直径：diameter</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">周长；perimeter</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">面积；area</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Author: ting shuo</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Date:2024-12-29</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">form math <span class="keyword">import</span> pi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>导入完了以后，我们需要用户输入，python处理，再输出</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> math <span class="keyword">import</span> pi</span><br><span class="line">radius = <span class="built_in">float</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入半径：&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">perimeter = <span class="number">2</span>*pi*radius</span><br><span class="line">area = pi*radius**<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;圆的周长为：&quot;</span>,<span class="built_in">round</span>(perimeter,<span class="number">2</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;圆的面积为：&quot;</span>,<span class="built_in">round</span>(area,<span class="number">2</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>[!IMPORTANT]</p><p>因为input函数会使输入的参数变为字符串，不能直接进行计算<br>所以要记得将其转化为浮点数或整数</p></blockquote><p>效果如下：</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tingshuo-yiqing/PicGo-tuchuang/img/20241229184326150.png" style="zoom:50%;" /><h3 id="2-字符串-string-的常见操作"><a href="#2-字符串-string-的常见操作" class="headerlink" title="2.字符串(string)的常见操作"></a>2.字符串(string)的常见操作</h3><ul><li>求字符串长度用<code>len()</code>函数也就是length，这里可以用来求平均数</li></ul><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nums_list = [<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">6</span>,<span class="number">7</span>,<span class="number">8</span>,<span class="number">9</span>,]</span><br><span class="line">average = <span class="built_in">sum</span>(nums_list)/<span class="built_in">len</span>(nums_list)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(average)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>字符串的大小写，即首字母大写</li></ul><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">variable =  <span class="string">&quot;ting shuo&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(variable.title())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>字符串的类型转换</li></ul><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">### 3.简单的条件转换</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">即将给出的条件翻译过来</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">如：找到<span class="number">2000</span>年至<span class="number">3200</span>年（包含<span class="number">3200</span>）中的所有**可被<span class="number">7</span>整除但不能被<span class="number">5</span>整除的所有数字，得到的数字用分号隔开**，打印**一行**出来。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; 条件一：所有</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt; 条件二：可被<span class="number">7</span>整除但不能被<span class="number">5</span>整除</span><br><span class="line">&gt; 条件三：一行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">所以我们就要把条件转换为编程语言，一看到除法就要想到取余符号`%`，一行就是不换行`end=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>`</span><br><span class="line">`end=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>`是`<span class="built_in">print</span>()`的参数主要用于决定输出后是什么，`end=`默认是换行符`\n`</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; [!TIP]</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt; 这里我们会用到**格式化字符串字面量**也就是`<span class="string">f&quot;&quot;</span>`,这里f就是格式<span class="built_in">format</span>的意思</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```python</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#利用end=&quot;,&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">2000</span>,<span class="number">3201</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> i%<span class="number">7</span> == <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> i%<span class="number">5</span> i= <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;<span class="subst">&#123;i&#125;</span>&quot;</span>,end=<span class="string">&quot;,&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#利用f&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">2000</span>,<span class="number">3201</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> i%<span class="number">7</span> == <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> i%<span class="number">5</span> i= <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;<span class="subst">&#123;i&#125;</span>,&quot;</span>end=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>两者结果一致效果如下：</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tingshuo-yiqing/PicGo-tuchuang/img/20241230234044708.png" style="zoom:50%;" /><p>这两种方法都差不多，还有一种更快的方法</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#列表推导式，要快的多</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;,&#x27;</span>.join(<span class="built_in">str</span>(i) <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">2000</span>, <span class="number">3201</span>) <span class="keyword">if</span> i % <span class="number">7</span> == <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> i % <span class="number">5</span>!= <span class="number">0</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
